---
title: Sri Lankan Style Lentil Sambar Curry with Roasted Aubergine, Zesty Rice and Peanuts
description: Our Sri Lankan Style Lentil Sambar Curry is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221111_R40_W51_UK_R3572-19_KB_Main_low-24216c6a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sri-lankan-style-lentil-sambar-curry-634ec91c95b1ef8612fd5036-eaa517d4.pdf
cuisine: Sri Lankesisk
nutrition:
  calories: 790 kcal
